headline: High Growth Tech Stocks To Watch In US This October 2025
summary: As of late October 2025, the U.S. stock market has seen mixed performances with significant developments such as Nvidia reaching a $5 trillion market cap and Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell indicating uncertainty over future interest rate cuts. In this dynamic environment, identifying high-growth tech stocks involves looking for companies that can capitalize on technological advancements and maintain robust growth despite potential economic headwinds.

headline: Metro Bank selects Infosys and Workday to transform finance operations
summary: Metro Bank will transition from older financial systems to a cloud-based platform using a suite of Workday financial management tools.
